  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>KID PILOT</i></strong> is a VR flying game where every level you unlock is unique and fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/7ee9454b709742a3365a7887c77de562.poster.avif?t=1740424716\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/7ee9454b709742a3365a7887c77de562.webm?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/7ee9454b709742a3365a7887c77de562.mp4?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>FLY & SHOOT</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gameplay is straight-forward. Move the plane with your hand and shoot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/086a39d3ac18591241579167458be8a6.poster.avif?t=1740424716\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/086a39d3ac18591241579167458be8a6.webm?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/086a39d3ac18591241579167458be8a6.mp4?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>COMPLETE CHALLENGES</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the game, you will encounter harder challenges to put your pilot abilities to the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/5963b36f7160cca88ef205287d0fa955.poster.avif?t=1740424716\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/5963b36f7160cca88ef205287d0fa955.webm?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/5963b36f7160cca88ef205287d0fa955.mp4?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>EPIC BOSS FIGHTS!</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who doesn’t love epic bosses? <strong><i>KID PILOT</i></strong> is no exception, so be ready to be challenged.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/7a0f598e75bf5bc5617d9607f38d26eb.poster.avif?t=1740424716\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/7a0f598e75bf5bc5617d9607f38d26eb.webm?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/7a0f598e75bf5bc5617d9607f38d26eb.mp4?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>UNIQUE LEVELS</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No two levels are the same! Can you complete them all? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/704b20809ba0fdcebc26a7bf64b13977.poster.avif?t=1740424716\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/704b20809ba0fdcebc26a7bf64b13977.webm?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/704b20809ba0fdcebc26a7bf64b13977.mp4?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>KID PILOT</i></strong> is a VR flying game where every level you unlock is unique and fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/7ee9454b709742a3365a7887c77de562.poster.avif?t=1740424716\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/7ee9454b709742a3365a7887c77de562.webm?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/7ee9454b709742a3365a7887c77de562.mp4?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>FLY & SHOOT</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gameplay is straight-forward. Move the plane with your hand and shoot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/086a39d3ac18591241579167458be8a6.poster.avif?t=1740424716\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/086a39d3ac18591241579167458be8a6.webm?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/086a39d3ac18591241579167458be8a6.mp4?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>COMPLETE CHALLENGES</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the game, you will encounter harder challenges to put your pilot abilities to the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/5963b36f7160cca88ef205287d0fa955.poster.avif?t=1740424716\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/5963b36f7160cca88ef205287d0fa955.webm?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/5963b36f7160cca88ef205287d0fa955.mp4?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>EPIC BOSS FIGHTS!</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who doesn’t love epic bosses? <strong><i>KID PILOT</i></strong> is no exception, so be ready to be challenged.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/7a0f598e75bf5bc5617d9607f38d26eb.poster.avif?t=1740424716\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/7a0f598e75bf5bc5617d9607f38d26eb.webm?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/7a0f598e75bf5bc5617d9607f38d26eb.mp4?t=1740424716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>UNIQUE LEVELS</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No two levels are the same! Can you complete them all? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2484570/extras/704b20809ba0fdcebc26a7bf64b1